c: 11
v: 5
t: "Oobbiya! Diggah ama koros sinni alilwat koroosannu qellissam, usun Yallak ken alilwat tanim qellisaanam akkaluk, oobbiya!Ama koros mataaxiga sinni sarat yambududen waqdi Yalli usun qellisaanam kee yaybulleenim inkih keenik yaaxigem, diggah Yalli ken alilwat qellitti ittam yaaxigi kinni"